#: views/option-tabs/faq-tab.php:78
msgid "How does Breeze handle WordPress multisite?"
msgstr "¿Cómo gestiona Breeze un WordPress multisitio?"

#: views/option-tabs/faq-tab.php:80
msgid "Breeze handles all WordPress multisite instances globally. All the settings for multisite are now handled on the network level."
msgstr "Breeze maneja todas las instancias de un WordPress multisitio de manera global. Ahora, todos los ajustes del multisitio se manejan a nivel de red."

#: views/option-tabs/faq-tab.php:203
msgid "KnowledgeBase article for details."
